title: Project Memory — Atlas Migration
meta: | type: memory

section: Context
context: id: ctx-01 | scope: project | confidence: high | text: Migrating legacy monolith to Kubernetes microservices by 2025-12-15.
context: id: ctx-02 | scope: team | confidence: high | text: Core team: Priya, Sam, Wei, Jules.

section: Decisions
decision: id: dec-01 | scope: architecture | confidence: high | text: Use Postgres for transactions, ClickHouse for analytics.
decision: id: dec-02 | scope: infra | confidence: medium | text: Adopt ArgyoCD for GitOps deploys.

section: Constraints
constraint: id: con-01 | scope: regulatory | confidence: high | text: PII must remain in EU-region databases.

section: Risks
risk: id: risk-01 | scope: data | confidence: medium | text: Schema drift between legacy and new order service.